SolitudePantherBeholderRing0401.name: Solitude Panther Beholder Ring #0401
Creed: The Solitude Panther Association has granted you the beholder
this token of appreciation.
This ring will grant you access through the gates of wisdom
wealth and knowledge.
When the time comes, you the beholder will know what to do
with it.
Remember you are fighting for what matters most to you.
If we stand united, not anxious nor blinded by the light,
we shall conquer all we set out to do.
